Invocation Name: image inception
des:
Image Inception brings you the power of OpenAI's amazing DALL-E image creator through any Alexa device.

Ask for any image you can imagine and it will create it and email it to you.

Each image created consumes one credit. You are given credits for free to start and can purchase more when you need them.

-----
